  "title": "IT Infrastructure Engineer (Support sale/Presale, Up $6K)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Location: Chai Chee</strong><br /><strong>Skillset: Microsoft, AWS, Google Cloud CSP Licensing, Azure</strong><br /><strong>Mon to Fri 8.30am to 5.30pm</strong><br /><strong>With AWS & Bonus</strong><br /><strong></strong></p><p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Microsoft, AWS, Google Cloud CSP Licensing</li><li>Cloud Admin-as-a-Service (CloudOps Lite)</li><li>Infrastructure Management-as-a-Service (IFMaaS)</li><li>End User Computing Management-as-a-Service (EUCMaaS)</li><li>Network Management-as-a-Service (firewall, WiFi, SD-WAN)</li><li>M365, Azure, Exchange service packages</li><li>On-prem to cloud transition services</li><li>Hybrid infrastructure managed services</li><li>Own the full As-A-Service product portfolio across Cloud, Network, End-User, and Hybrid Infrastructure domains.</li><li>Develop product roadmaps aligned with customer demand, market trends, and organisational strategy.</li><li>Support Sales and Pre-Sales with product positioning, customer pitches, tender submissions, and commercial structuring</li></ul><p><br /><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Degree in Information Technology, Business, Engineering, or equivalent.</li><li>Professional certifications such as Azure Fundamentals, AWS Cloud Practitioner, Google Cloud Digital Leader, ITIL, or equivalent is advantageous.</li><li>3–6 years of experience in product management, cloud services, managed services, or IT commercial roles.</li><li>Experience with CSP subscription management, cloud infrastructure (Azure/AWS/GCP), and IT managed service offerings.</li></ul><p><u><strong>Only shortlisted candidates will be notified</strong></u>\nPlease submit your updated resume in MS format by using the <strong>APPLY NOW BUTTON.</strong><br />Alternatively, you may also email your resume to us at <a href=\"mailto:emily.fong@atomrecruit.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>emily.fong@atomrecruit.com</strong></a></p><p><strong>Emily Fong</strong><br /><strong>Senior Talent Specialist</strong>\nAtomrecruit Pte. Ltd. | MOM EA License No.: 15C7443\nEA Personnel Reg No.: R1768368</p>",
